{"h2d2b5c2cg10e8g4728gb2a1g6aa71eb804ed": ["How did Olly die, anyway?", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents_OllyDead.html", "1abe1e8f-0d65-ce61-6bc5-2ebb6570c411"], "h2324b088g2a47g4e54g91a2g54e50cd32d76": ["Painfully. I don't want to talk about it.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents_OllyDead.html", "8c327f5c-b4c1-f5b9-bb9a-5c1c5160a934"], "hf1ed899bgfa62g47d5ga043ge699c78e26c9": ["When we set off, I want you at the front of the convoy. ", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents_OllyDead.html", "29c8cf74-872f-58e6-1bfa-dfe488e371d9"], "hd43211b6gf710g4811ga892ga14ab1a125c7": ["No thank you. I'm a rear-guard man, always have been. ", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents_OllyDead.html", "deb37a83-295d-5693-90d5-c8a3e0328f59"], "h5aef6689g2a01g4368gb2bbgb39ab38e5c5a": ["If we leave you behind,  is that rear enough?", "8a064abd-3582-4a32-a9f8-748ad60f63ca", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents_OllyDead.html", "3e05ddd1-d6be-ba8f-a7b5-9c682daba7f6"], "h1f304ed8gc828g4e45ga35bgb16e639e531d": ["You drive a hard bargain. The middle it is. ", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_AD_ZhentShipmentAgents_OllyDead.html", "5a5daece-412b-ef6e-e674-1c5d4613564c"]}